'''Section 19''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] agency that produced classified starship designs for the Galactic Empire.

==History==
Some of their ship designs were believed to have included active [[Cloaking device/Legends|cloaking devices]]. During the [[Black Fleet Crisis]], the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] investigated a hyperspace comm device that could have been made by the Section during the heydays of the Empire.

